----------------------------------------------------
			AccountGUISuperClass
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities		
----------------------------------------------------
Manages the communication between GUIs that have to
	do with user accounts and the AccountManager
----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators		
----------------------------------------------------
AccountManager
----------------------------------------------------



----------------------------------------------------
				AccountScreen
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities		
----------------------------------------------------
Gives options for the user to go to
- Start game
- Edit their account
- Log out
- Return to the StartScreen
