----------------------------------------------------



----------------------------------------------------
				MainFrame
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities		
----------------------------------------------------
Displays the screen where the hangman game is played.
Has an inputfield where letters and words can be typed
Has a place where the gallow and hangman are displayed
Has a place where the current player and avatar are displayed
Has a placed where the guessed letters are displayed
Has options for return to the menu and to restart
----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators		
----------------------------------------------------
GameLoop
GUISuperClass
Hangman
----------------------------------------------------



----------------------------------------------------
				OptionScreen
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities		
Displays the screen where the options can be changed.
Has a slider with which the difficulty of the game can be set.
Has a slider with which the sound volume level can be set.
The game can be started with a button.
User can return to menu with a button.
----------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators		
----------------------------------------------------
GUISuperClass
SoundPlayer
GameManager
----------------------------------------------------



----------------------------------------------------
				PopUpWindow
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities			
----------------------------------------------------
Show losing or winning message
Show the correct word
Show the amount of points
OK button to close the popup
----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators		
----------------------------------------------------
GameLoop
----------------------------------------------------



----------------------------------------------------
				StartScreen
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities		
----------------------------------------------------
Display option to start the game
Display option to log in 
Display option to go to options
Display option to create a new account
Display option to view highscores
Display option to exit
----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators		
----------------------------------------------------
CreateAccount
OptionScreen
HighscoreScreen
LoginScreen
AccountWindow
----------------------------------------------------





