----------------------------------------------------
			  AbstractInput
----------------------------------------------------
	Responsibilities
----------------------------------------------------
Abstract superclass for InputWord and InputLetter
Implements Input interface
Get guess string
Check whether guess is a letter
----------------------------------------------------
	Collaborators
----------------------------------------------------
Input
----------------------------------------------------



